Transcription.Text: Chapter four. Everyone in Gallows Corner spoke of it as a whirlwind engagement when it was announced two weeks later that Carolines Dodd had be- come engaged to David Carson. Caroline had never been made love to by such an experienced man as David Carson, he literally swept her off her feet.
